com.streetsofboston.smugmug.v1_2_1.system
Class Account

java.lang.Object
  com.streetsofboston.smugmug.v1_2_1.system.Account

public class Account
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents a User account on Smugmug. It is also called a 'session-account', since it is always tied to a Session.

Author:
Anton Spaans

sessionReestablished

public void sessionReestablished(Session previousSession)
This method should not be called if you're not developing/extending this API. This method is called when a session is re-established after a re-login.

Parameters:
previousSession - Use this to obtain information from the previous (invalid) session.
